class Node:

    def __init__(self, value):
        self.value = value
        self.left = None
        self.right = None

def binarySearchTree(items):
    if not items:
        return None
    mid = len(items) / 2
    rootValue = items[mid]
    root = Node(rootValue)
    root.left = binarySearchTree(items[:mid])
    root.right = binarySearchTree(items[mid + 1:])
    return root
